                <div class="methods__founder-name">Chris Kincade</div>
            </div>
            <div class="methods__founder">
                <div class="methods__founder-avatar methods__founder-avatar--am">AM</div>
                <div class="methods__founder-name">Ari Meisel</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="methods__tabs reveal" id="methodTabs">
            <button class="methods__tab is-active" data-system="innovation">Innovation System</button>
            <button class="methods__tab" data-system="optimization">Optimization System</button>
            <button class="methods__tab" data-system="cognitive">Cognitive System</button>
        </div>

        <div class="methods__system is-active" data-panel="innovation">
            <div class="methods__fw reveal">
                <div class="methods__fw-head"><span class="methods__fw-code">ID10</span><span class="methods__fw-title">Value-Centric Design</span></div>
                <div class="methods__fw-author">Chris Kincade</div>
                <div class="methods__fw-desc">Conversational excavation of who you are — creates Cultural, Product, Customer, and Market Values, plus Dual Metrics drafts (ID20–23; LA20–21).</div>
            </div>
            <div class="methods__fw reveal reveal-d1">
                <div class="methods__fw-head"><span class="methods__fw-code">MA10</span><span class="methods__fw-title">Open Road Canvas</span></div>
                <div class="methods__fw-author">Chris Kincade</div>
                <div class="methods__fw-desc">Strategic positioning that defines where you compete and how you win — creates Competitive Positioning, Business Model, and Revenue Strategy (MA20–22).</div>
            </div>
            <div class="methods__fw reveal reveal-d2">
                <div class="methods__fw-head"><span class="methods__fw-code">IN10</span><span class="methods__fw-title">Value Mapping</span></div>
                <div class="methods__fw-author">Chris Kincade</div>
                <div class="methods__fw-desc">Defines what you're building and how you're expanding — creates Product Roadmap and Growth Strategy (IN20–21).</div>
            </div>
            <div class="methods__fw reveal reveal-d3">
                <div class="methods__fw-head"><span class="methods__fw-code">BR10</span><span class="methods__fw-title">Impact Branding</span></div>
                <div class="methods__fw-author">Chris Kincade</div>
