            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="methods__system" data-panel="optimization">
            <div class="methods__fw reveal">
                <div class="methods__fw-head"><span class="methods__fw-code">PD10</span><span class="methods__fw-title">The Genius Paradigm</span></div>
                <div class="methods__fw-author">Ari Meisel</div>
                <div class="methods__fw-desc">Defines where you do your most strategic work — creates Innovation Zone and Task Replacement Plan (PD20–21).</div>
            </div>
            <div class="methods__fw reveal reveal-d1">
                <div class="methods__fw-head"><span class="methods__fw-code">WF10</span><span class="methods__fw-title">Smart Workflows</span></div>
                <div class="methods__fw-author">Ari Meisel</div>
                <div class="methods__fw-desc">Clarifies how work flows with minimal friction — creates Signal Clarity, Project Clarity, and Delegation Standards (WF20–22).</div>
            </div>
            <div class="methods__fw reveal reveal-d2">
                <div class="methods__fw-head"><span class="methods__fw-code">PR10</span><span class="methods__fw-title">Process Perfection</span></div>
                <div class="methods__fw-author">Ari Meisel</div>
                <div class="methods__fw-desc">Establishes Standing Operating Protocols (the AI-native SOP) — creates Process Clarity, OAO Methodology, and Quality Standards (PR20–22).</div>
            </div>
            <div class="methods__fw reveal reveal-d3">
                <div class="methods__fw-head"><span class="methods__fw-code">CU10</span><span class="methods__fw-title">Eight Traits of Endurance</span></div>
                <div class="methods__fw-author">Ari Meisel</div>
                <div class="methods__fw-desc">Establishes cultural practices that sustain performance — creates Cultural Framework, Leadership Development, and Team Structure (CU20–22).</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="methods__system" data-panel="cognitive">
            <div class="methods__fw reveal">
                <div class="methods__fw-head"><span class="methods__fw-code">SY10</span><span class="methods__fw-title">Smart Orgs</span></div>
                <div class="methods__fw-author">Chris Kincade</div>
                <div class="methods__fw-desc">AI-native organizational design — establishes System Configuration and governance protocols for Smart OS activation (SY21).</div>
            </div>
            <div class="methods__fw reveal reveal-d1">
                <div class="methods__fw-head"><span class="methods__fw-code">LA10</span><span class="methods__fw-title">Organizational Intelligence</span></div>
                <div class="methods__fw-author">Chris Kincade</div>
                <div class="methods__fw-desc">Builds the measurement layer — creates Empirical Metrics and Empathic Metrics as Autonomic Equations (LA20–21).</div>
            </div>
            <div class="methods__fw reveal reveal-d2">
                <div class="methods__fw-head"><span class="methods__fw-code">IT10</span><span class="methods__fw-title">Activating Your Smart OS</span></div>
                <div class="methods__fw-author">Chris Kincade</div>
