            </div>
            <div class="methods__fw reveal reveal-d3">
                <div class="methods__fw-head"><span class="methods__fw-code">SY11</span><span class="methods__fw-title">Unlocking Deep Context</span></div>
                <div class="methods__fw-author">Chris Kincade</div>
